# Cowork Forge - AI Context Snapshot
# Purpose: Minimal context for AI agents to understand project structure

## PROJECT OVERVIEW

name: cowork-forge
type: rust-workspace
edition: "2024"
version: "2.5.0"
description: AI-native iterative software development platform with multi-agent orchestration

## CRATES STRUCTURE

### cowork-core
path: crates/cowork-core/
role: domain-logic-core
description: Core library with domain entities, pipeline orchestration, tools, persistence
key_modules:
  - pipeline: 7-stage workflow orchestration
  - domain: Project, Iteration, Memory aggregates (DDD)
  - tools: 30+ ADK tools
  - persistence: JSON-based storage
  - interaction: CLI/GUI abstraction
  - agents: Agent builders
  - instructions: Prompts for each stage

### cowork-cli
path: crates/cowork-cli/
role: cli-adapter
commands: [init, iter, list, show, continue, status, delete, import, knowledge, config]

### cowork-gui
path: crates/cowork-gui/
role: gui-adapter
description: Tauri + React desktop application

## CORE CONCEPTS

### 7-Stage Pipeline

| Stage | HITL | Output |
|-------|------|--------|
| idea | No | idea.md |
| prd | Yes | prd.md |
| design | Yes | design.md |
| plan | Yes | plan.md |
| coding | Yes | workspace/ |
| check | No | check_report.md |
| delivery | No | delivery_report.md |

### Iteration Types
- **Genesis**: First iteration, fresh start
- **Evolution**: Build upon previous iteration

### Actor-Critic Pattern
Critical stages use Actor-Critic loop:
Actor generates → Critic validates → HITL confirms

---

## STORAGE STRUCTURE

```
.cowork-v2/
├── project.json              # Project metadata
├── memory.json               # ProjectMemory
└── iterations/
    └── iter-<number>-<timestamp>/
        ├── iteration.json    # Iteration metadata
        ├── memory.json       # IterationKnowledge
        ├── artifacts/
        │   ├── idea.md
        │   ├── prd.md
        │   ├── design.md
        │   ├── plan.md
        │   └── delivery_report.md
        ├── workspace/        # Generated code
        └── summaries/        # Document summaries
```

### Store Implementations

| Store | File | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| ProjectStore | `persistence/project_store.rs` | project.json |
| IterationStore | `persistence/iteration_store.rs` | iterations/* |
| MemoryStore | `persistence/memory_store.rs` | memory.json |

### Workspace Preparation (Evolution)

| Inheritance | What's Copied |
|-------------|---------------|
| None | Fresh workspace |
| Partial | Artifacts only |
| Full | Artifacts + workspace |

