## CRITICAL PATHS

| Task | Entry Point |
|------|-------------|
| Execute iteration | `IterationExecutor::execute()` |
| Stage execution | `Stage::execute()` |
| HITL confirmation | `InteractiveBackend::request_input()` |
| Tool registry | `tools/mod.rs` |

